{"type":"message","id":"de310f0a","parentId":"625d6fb5","timestamp":"2026-03-27T21:40:15.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've successfully completed the autonomous learning task. The learning note has been saved to the specified file. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"f9b7b7ffc3e91491d0e61516d74006dddd8112aa6cf020fa2e4c249fb70bf45e"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n自主学习已完成。检测到5分钟内无活跃对话（仅有cron任务自身session），已执行学习。\n\n**执行摘要**：\n- 搜索了3个领域的最新动态：企业数字化转型政策、智能安防弱电工程趋势、IT运维与网络系统集成趋势\n- 整理了5条关键信息（含政策补贴节点、技术趋势、市场格局、服务模式转型等）\n- 已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4824,"output":135,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48940,"cost":{"input":0.0014471999999999998,"output":0.00016199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029286299999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774647609808}}
